comments.text:
1970s  The 747 Era
		1970: Pan Am Flight93 (Boeing747121) hijacked & destroyed  hull loss, no fatalities onboard after evacuation.  
		1973: Japan Airlines Flight404 (747) hijacked & destroyed.  
		1974: Lufthansa Flight540 (747100) crashed after takeoff  ~59 deaths.  
		1977: Tenerife collision (Pan Am & KLM 747s)  583 fatalities.  
		1978: Air India Flight855 (747200) crashed off Mumbai  213 fatalities.  



 1980s  HighFatality 747 Disasters
		1980: Korean Air Lines Flight015 (747) crashed on landing  15 deaths.  
		1983:
		Pan Am Flight73 (747)  runway accident, hull loss.
		KAL007 (747) shot down  269 deaths.
		Avianca Flight011 (747) crash near Madrid  181 fatalities.  
		1985:
		Air India Flight182 bombing (747)  329 deaths.
		JAL Flight123 (747SR)  520 deaths (single-aircraft worst accident ever).  
		1987: SAA Flight295 (747200 Combi) cargo fire/crash  159 fatalities.  
		1988: Pan Am Flight103 Lockerbie bombing (747)  259 onboard + 11 ground fatalities.  
		1989: Flying Tiger Line Flight66 (747200F) crash in Malaysia  4 fatalities.



 1990s
		Hull-loss accidents with fewer fatalities occurred (e.g., China Airlines Flight605 runway overrun in 1993).  



 2000s  Boeing 737 Tragedies
		2007: Adam Air Flight574 (737400) crashed in Indonesia  102 fatalities.  
		2010:
		Air India Express Flight812 (737800) runway overrun  158 deaths.  
		UPS 747400 freighter crash in Dubai  2 crew deaths.



 2010s
		2008: British Airways Flight38 (777200ER) crash at Heathrow  hull loss, 47 injuries, no fatalities.  
		2013: Dreamliner battery fires led to global grounding.
		2018: Lion Air Flight610 (737 MAX 8) crashed in Java Sea  189 fatalities.   
		2019: Ethiopian Airlines Flight302 (737 MAX 8) crash  157 fatalities.  



 2020s
		2020: Air India Express Flight1344 (737) overrun in Kozhikode  ~21 fatalities.
		2022: China Eastern Flight5735 (737800) nosedive near Guangxi  132 fatalities.
		20232024 (737 MAX non-fatal incidents):
		Ryanair Flight1269 (2023)  sudden altitude drop, no deaths.
		Alaska Airlines Flight1282 (2024)  cabin decompression, 3 injuries.   
		Southwest Flight746 (2024)  Dutch roll yaw event.
		Korean Air Flight189 (2024)  pressurization failure, 13 injured.   
		2025:
		Air India Flight171 (7878) crash in Ahmedabad  241 fatalities, 1 survivor. First-ever deadly Dreamliner crash.
